# Pillar — Performance Efficiency

*Hit performance targets without overspending.*

## Checklist

- **Right compute** — Lambda (sporadic) · Fargate (steady) · EC2 (sustained) · **Graviton** (~20% price/perf)
- **Right data engine per pattern** — RDS/Aurora OLTP · DynamoDB key-value · Redshift warehouse · S3+Athena lake · OpenSearch search · ElastiCache hot
- **Cache** — CloudFront (edge) · ElastiCache (app) · **DAX** (DynamoDB)
- **Async** — SQS / SNS / EventBridge / Step Functions decouple slow work
- **Auto-scale** on the right metric, with cooldowns (no thrash)

## Principles

Managed services · global in minutes · serverless · experiment · mechanical sympathy

**Core move:** **match the tool to the access pattern** — the most-tested idea. No universal "best."
